      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i hear you but i'm just trying to avoid the hassle. if the bleeding has slowed to a trickle and it's not that deep where i can see the fat or anything, can't i just clean it with some antiseptic and then use the honey as a natural barrier? like, is there really any risk of it getting way worse if i just manage it myself tonight and see how it looks in the morning?",
